text: Pia Carmen Maria Lionetti is an Italian archer. She was born on 26 February 1987. Lionetti competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and 2012 Summer Olympics.Pia LionettiPia LIONETTI == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Italian archers Category:Olympians for Italy Category:Sportspeople from Apulia
